## Obecny stan (2026)

**Live — daily loop:**
- `vanguard-morning-brief` → plan jutra rano
- `vanguard-midday-check` → inline buttons (done/stuck)
- `vanguard-daily-reconciliation` → wieczorny review
- `vanguard-telegram` → stream + reconciliation routing + **planning sessions** (Oracle)
- Planning zapisuje `planning_summary` z tension_action na jutro

**Live — evidence layer:**
- friction_events + confirmed_friction_events VIEW
- vanguard-auto-classify, vanguard-architect, vanguard-analyst
- vanguard-oracle z full state vector (Oura, wins, plan)

- Osobny Telegram bot, Day 0 baseline + Day 1+ eval

~~Observation mode~~ — **deprecated**. System jest w pełnym daily loop, nie w trybie zbierania danych.

